1311
02:13:04,108 --> 02:13:07,308
...minus percent.

1312
02:13:11,208 --> 02:13:15,108
And because we just defeated the raid boss...

1313
02:13:15,808 --> 02:13:19,608
...it was a special roulette that's mostly positive.

1314
02:13:26,708 --> 02:13:32,108
So basically everything went up. It's...

1315
02:13:32,108 --> 02:13:35,108
