1348
02:17:19,216 --> 02:17:21,216
Yes.

1349
02:17:23,216 --> 02:17:26,216
And then this one is fine.

1350
02:17:42,216 --> 02:17:46,216
Yeah, and I always see like these like tricks that people are like,

1351
02:17:46,216 --> 02:17:50,216
"If the watermelon sounds like this when you hit this part of the watermelon, it's a good watermelon." I'm just like,

1352
