1356
02:18:13,216 --> 02:18:18,216
...situations where I got the watermelon, and it's just not that great.

1357
02:18:18,716 --> 02:18:19,716
Okay.

1358
02:18:20,216 --> 02:18:22,216
We go town, we sell.

